# Passwordless sudo for the default ftw user.
#
# Mirrors what stage2 ships for `pi` on a stock Raspberry Pi OS
# Lite build. Without this file, ftw has no admin rights at all
# and cannot run `sudo systemctl status …` for diagnostics, which
# is the recovery path documented in docs/rpi-image.md.
#
# Owner-paranoid file mode (0440) — sudo refuses to load fragments
# that are world-writable.
ftw ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL
